31#include "mech_locl.h"
32
33GSSAPI_LIB_FUNCTION OM_uint32 GSSAPI_LIB_CALL
34gss_inquire_names_for_mech(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
35 const gss_OID mechanism,
36 gss_OID_set *name_types)
37{
38 OM_uint32 major_status;
39 gssapi_mech_interface m = __gss_get_mechanism(mechanism);
40
41 *minor_status = 0;
42 *name_types = GSS_C_NO_OID_SET;
43 if (!m)
44 return (GSS_S_BAD_MECH);
45
46 /*
47 * If the implementation can do it, ask it for a list of
48 * names, otherwise fake it.
49 */
50 if (m->gm_inquire_names_for_mech) {
51 return (m->gm_inquire_names_for_mech(minor_status,
52 mechanism, name_types));
53 } else {
54 major_status = gss_create_empty_oid_set(minor_status,
55 name_types);
56 if (major_status)
57 return (major_status);
58 major_status = gss_add_oid_set_member(minor_status,
59 GSS_C_NT_HOSTBASED_SERVICE, name_types);
60 if (major_status) {
61 OM_uint32 junk;
62 gss_release_oid_set(&junk, name_types);
63 return (major_status);
64 }
65 major_status = gss_add_oid_set_member(minor_status,
66 GSS_C_NT_USER_NAME, name_types);
67 if (major_status) {
68 OM_uint32 junk;
69 gss_release_oid_set(&junk, name_types);
70 return (major_status);
71 }
72 }
73
74 return (GSS_S_COMPLETE);
75}
